w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jeff_goldblum_press-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jeff_goldblum_press-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-goldblum">杰夫·戈德布鲁姆（Jeff Goldblum）</a>宣布了他的新专辑“ Still Blooming”，该专辑将以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">Ariana Grande</a> ，Cynthia Erivo和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/scarlett-johansson">Scarlett Johansson</a>出现。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="872" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/big-read-jeff-goldblum-sex-drugs-jazz-piano-2400542"><b>大读物 - 杰夫·戈德布鲁姆（Jeff Goldblum）：性与毒品和爵士钢琴</b></a></li></ul><p>他的第四张录音室专辑总共看到他与Mildred Snitzer乐团团聚，并将于4月25日通过Decca发行。您可以<a href="https://jeffgoldblum.lnk.to/stillblooming" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订/预添加您的副本。</p><p> Goldblum还分享了唱片的主打单曲“ Best Is The Bot The Bot Boun”，其中包括Johansson的客串人声。这是赛·科尔曼（Cy Coleman）1959年作品的封面，该作品在1964年由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-sinatra">弗兰克·辛纳</a>屈（Frank Sinatra）闻名。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Jeff Goldblum和Mildred Snitzer乐团壮举。斯嘉丽·约翰逊（Scarlett Johansson） - 最好的是" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/d84Id8fPs3I?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>戈德布鲁姆（Goldblum）和约翰逊（Johansson）都出现在2017年的漫威电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/thor-ragnarok-film-review-2153343"><i>《雷神：拉格纳克》（Thor：Ragnarok）</i></a>中，并且还在韦斯·<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/wes-anderson">安德森（Wes Anderson</a> ） <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/isle-of-dogs-wes-anderson-film-review-2275948#:~:text=His%20latest%20project%2C%20Isle%20Of,will%20struggle%20to%20find%20fault."><i>的狗</i></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/asteroid-city"><i>小行星城市</i></a>中彼此出演。约翰逊还培养了自己的音乐事业，包括专辑《 2008年的我躺下》和第二年的皮特·伊恩（Pete Yorn）的“分手”。</p><p> “仍在盛开”还看到Goldblum与他的两位<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><i>邪恶的</i></a>联合主演，Grande在开场的曲目中唱歌“我不知道为什么（我只是愿意）”，而Erivo在歌曲中的功能“我们将再次见面” 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3833707" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833707" style="width: 1359px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833707" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Still-Blooming.jpg" alt="" width="1359" height="1355" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Still-Blooming.jpg 1359w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Still-Blooming-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Still-Blooming-400x399.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Still-Blooming-800x798.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Still-Blooming-696x694.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Still-Blooming-1068x1065.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1359px) 100vw, 1359px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833707" class="wp-caption-text">杰夫·戈德布鲁姆（Jeff Goldblum）和米尔德雷德（Mildred Snitzer）乐团 - “仍在开花”专辑艺术</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“仍在盛开”曲目列表：</strong> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="871" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot